  "remarks": "Shandong OreeLaser Technology Co., Ltd is a Chinese entity specialised in the manufacturing of machine tools. In particular through the Russian group “Intervesp Company”, it supplies laser-cutting machine tools on the Russian market. Such machine tools are necessary for Russia’s military and industrial complex. Therefore, Shandong OreeLaser Co., Ltd is supporting Russia’s military and industrial complex and is furthermore associated with Intervesp-M LLC and LLC Intervesp Company.",
